844
00:47:52,637 --> 00:47:53,671
So goodbye.

845
00:47:53,771 --> 00:47:55,340
Goodbye.

846
00:47:55,440 --> 00:47:56,674
Eleanor, come on.

847
00:47:56,774 --> 00:47:58,009
Please.

848
00:47:58,109 --> 00:47:59,978
