897
00:50:04,969 --> 00:50:05,770
OK.

898
00:50:05,870 --> 00:50:06,737
I won't worry about it.

899
00:50:06,837 --> 00:50:08,239
I'm not worried about it.

900
00:50:08,339 --> 00:50:09,374
Good.

901
00:50:09,474 --> 00:50:11,942
