I forgot how bad
Bolia's cooking is.

1047
00:56:27,084 --> 00:56:28,419
This stuff tastes like gravel.

1048
00:56:28,519 --> 00:56:31,155
Want me to ask her to
fix you something else?

1049
00:56:31,255 --> 00:56:31,889
Nah.

1050
00:56:31,989 --> 00:56:33,123
She's nice.

1051
