00:57:51,201 --> 00:57:52,903
What'd I tell you?

1082
00:57:53,003 --> 00:57:54,171
Good, huh?

1083
00:57:54,271 --> 00:57:55,740
Amazing!

1084
00:57:55,840 --> 00:57:58,075
I can feel the MSG in my toes.

1085
00:57:58,175 --> 00:57:59,209
Oh, yeah.

